name: UNNAMED
description:
You - an UNNAMED suicide with a question mark instead of a face.
But it looks like dying won't be so easy. Help the poor man to realize his dream.

By pressing the key combination "W-A-S-D" and "ENTER", you can control the main UNNAMED character.

Mini game:
Exploring a gloomy world and solving simple puzzles, find out the end of this story.

Features:
Unusual logic
Unusual style
